and $f$ is defined as:

:$f = \set {\tuple {a, p}, \tuple {b, p}, \tuple {c, q}, \tuple {i, r}, \tuple {j, s}, \tuple {k, s} }$


Thus the images of each of the elements of $S$ under $f$ are:

{{begin-eqn}}
